OL,7,FITV West Country reporter Sam
OL,8,FBlackledge sits down with one woman
OL,9,Fwho was allegedly assaulted by a
OL,10,Fmember of Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,12,FA woman who was allegedly assaulted by
OL,13,Fa police officer has claimed she was
OL,14,Fpainted as 'the offender' and had her
OL,15,Fcase covered up by by the force.
OL,17,FJessica* spoke to ITV News about how
OL,18,Fshe believes Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,19,Fhas buried numerous cases of abuse by
OL,20,Fit's officers and how she has now
OL,21,F'lost all faith' in the them.
