OL,7,FHer ordeal began five-and-a-half years
OL,8,Fago when she was abused a member of
OL,9,Fthe force - who has since retired and
OL,10,Fdenies the allegations - "without any
OL,11,Fwarning".
OL,13,F"He grabbed my wrist and attacked me
OL,14,Fin the doorway," Jessica, herself a
OL,15,Fretired officer, said.
