OL,3,C'I've lost all faith': Woman says
OL,4,Cpolice covered up abuse by their
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"I had no idea what was happening at
OL,8,Fall, I was screaming for help,
OL,9,Fscreaming for the police. He was
OL,10,Fpushing, shoving, pulling my hair,
OL,11,Fkicking me, and I didn't know why,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,FFollowing the incident she spoke to
OL,15,Fthe force - later finding out that her
OL,16,Fabuser had also spoken to officers at
OL,17,FDevon and Cornwall Police.
