OL,3,C'I've lost all faith': Woman says
OL,4,Cpolice covered up abuse by their
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FJessica said: "I phoned the police the
OL,8,Fnext day and I was told 'there was no
OL,9,Fassault'. And I said, 'there was an
OL,10,Fassault, I reported an assault and it
OL,11,Fshould have been recorded.' (But) I
OL,12,Fwas described as the offender."
OL,14,FThe case was investigated by officers
OL,15,Fand after three years, officers told
OL,16,FJessica she would face no further
OL,17,Faction and was cleared.
OL,19,FJessica: 'The police made no effort to
OL,20,Finvestigate... I've lost all faith in
OL,21,Fthe force'
