OL,7,FBut the lack of action against the
OL,8,Fofficer she accused of abusing her has
OL,9,Fled Jessica to believe that Devon and
OL,10,FCornwall Police intentionally covered
OL,11,Fup her case.
OL,13,FJessica said: "They made no effort to
OL,14,Finvestigate my assault. They waited
OL,15,Fthe six months and then told me they
OL,16,Fwere out of time to actually take any
OL,17,Faction against him."
