OL,3,C'I've lost all faith': Woman says
OL,4,Cpolice covered up abuse by their
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FShe added: "I've lost all faith in
OL,8,FDevon and Cornwall Police, I can't
OL,9,Ftrust them, I have no confidence in
OL,10,Fthem and I feel extremely let down.
OL,11,FThat's an understatement, I can't
OL,12,Fbegin to say how their treatment of
OL,13,Fme... has impacted on my life for the
OL,14,Flast five-and-a-half years.
OL,16,F"I have been diagnosed with PTSD (post
OL,17,Ftraumatic stress disorder) as a result
OL,18,Fof the assault, and I think that has
OL,19,Fthen been exaserbated by the way that
OL,20,FDevon and Cornwall (Police) did not
OL,21,Fdeal with that assault."
