OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FShe has now joined six other women
OL,8,Ftaking , with the case accusing the
OL,9,Fpolice of failing to investigate
OL,10,Freports of rape and stalking by
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThe civil case is being brought by the
OL,14,FCentre for Women's Justice (CWJ) on
OL,15,Fbehalf of the victims.
