OL,3,C'I've lost all faith': Woman says
OL,4,Cpolice covered up abuse by their
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FDebaleena Dasgupta, from the CWJ,
OL,8,Fsaid: "One of the things that the
OL,9,Fwomen have asked for from Devon and
OL,10,FCornwall Police is not just to settle
OL,11,Fthe claim in relation to them, but
OL,12,Factually have offered to come to the
OL,13,Ftable and talk to Devon and Cornwall
OL,14,FPolice about how they can improve
OL,15,Ftheir policies and practices so no-one
OL,16,Felse has to go through what they have
OL,17,Fbeen through."
