OL,3,C'I've lost all faith': Woman says
OL,4,Cpolice covered up abuse by their
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police has also
OL,8,Fresponded, confirming that they
OL,9,Freceived reports of the allegations
OL,10,Fabout ten days ago. It has since
OL,11,Freferred itself to the police
OL,12,Fwatchdog, the Independent Office for
OL,13,FPolice Conduct.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Assistant Chief
OL,16,FConstable Jim Pearce, said: "The IOPC
OL,17,Fhas asked for further work to be
OL,18,Fprogressed by the force before they
OL,19,Fcan accept and assess a referral, but
OL,20,Fwe remain in consultation with them in
OL,21,Fproviding the require information.
